data.description: Welcome to this enchanting Cape Cod cottage located in beautiful Spring Grove, Pennsylvania, where your Pinterest dreams can run wild. From the moment you step foot on this sprawling property, you'll be captivated by its picturesque beauty and timeless allure. This well maintained home boasts a generous 1,414 square feet of living space, providing ample room for you and your loved ones to create everlasting memories. Step inside, and be prepared to fall in love with the seamless blend of original hardwood floors and contemporary finishes. The warm and inviting living room, adorned with a cozy woodstove, beckons you to curl up with a good book on chilly evenings, while the abundance of natural light that streams through the windows bathes the entire space in a heavenly glow. And if you've ever dreamt of having your own farm-to-table experience, look no further than the backyard chicken coop, where you can raise your own chickens and enjoy fresh eggs every morning. Offering large mature Persimmon, Mulberry trees and Blackberry bushes. This captivating abode boasts three spacious bedrooms, each exuding a sense of comfort and elegance. The primary suite is very spacious. The remaining bedrooms, bathed in natural light, offer ample space for restful slumber or creative endeavors. Beyond the confines of the house, your imagination will run wild with the possibilities that this property holds. An expansive backyard, spanning over an acre, presents an idyllic canvas for outdoor entertaining and limitless adventures. Need not worry about the septic, new septic installed in 2022. Explore the lush grounds, envisioning your own secret garden or a tranquil meditation spot to escape the hustle and bustle of daily life. As if that weren't enough, this extraordinary offering also includes a three-car garage, a haven for car enthusiasts and hobbyists alike. The adjacent greenhouse and garden area provide the perfect opportunity to cultivate your green thumb, cultivating a bounty of fresh produce and colorful blooms, all within arm's reach. In this sanctuary of endless potential, the only limit is your imagination. Embrace the opportunity to create your own paradise, surrounded by the breathtaking beauty of Spring Grove. Don't miss out on this once-in-a-lifetime chance to own a slice of heaven – your dream home awaits!
